# EasySubmit.ai Project Rules

## Design System
- Primary Color: #12B3D1 
- Text Color: #1F2937
- Background: #F9FAFB
- Border Radius: 12px for all buttons, cards, and inputs.
- Tone: Empowered "Career Navigator" (professional, helpful, not robotic).

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router).
- State: Zustand (for onboarding and session data).
- Database/Auth: Prisma with Supabase.
- Icons: Lucide-React.

## Coding Preferences
- Use Functional Components and Tailwind CSS.
- For buttons, always use "Continue" instead of "Next".
- When using Nominatim API, always implement a debounce.
- Ensure all components are responsive.
- Extension UI must be injected via Shadow DOM to prevent CSS leaks.